{"tid":2388076,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"三十秒科學–控制肌肉重量的一隻蛋白酶","createTime":"2021-01-30T22:20:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-02T11:05:40.000Z","uid":38861,"like":28,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"38cc29482cabbf835f22c2e5fcfd0faae6fbba34","tid":2388076,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T22:20:13.000Z","msg":"肌肉大概佔據身體重量的40%。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5uAiuHk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5uAiuHk.jpg&h=a5e4519a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n踏入50歲後，平均每10年就會有15-30%的肌肉流失。<br />\n<br />\n（圖2）研究(Ref1)顯示老人家的肌肉裡頭，一隻名為15-PGDH的蛋白酶數量普遍地比年輕人為高。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VPJDuHw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVPJDuHw.png&h=911a492a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而15-PGDH其中一道作用就是負責將激素PGE2及PGD2分解成為其他物質。<br />\n<br />\n(圖3）而人類老化所出現的現象，老鼠亦能同樣發現得到。<br />\n除肌肉外，年長老鼠的心、肝、脾、大腸及皮膚亦出現15-PGDH蛋白酶上升的現象。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m3SHWnA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm3SHWnA.jpg&h=d91abf69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當利用藥物或基因工程手段降低年老老鼠的15-PGDH數量的話，肌肉重量亦會有所提升。<br />\n<br />\n相反，若強行在年輕老鼠肌肉裡頭強行表達15-PGDH的話，肌肉重量亦會有所下降。<br />\n<br />\n這道研究展示出，只需對一隻蛋白酶作出針對性的抑制，便能夠達到控制肌肉重量及結構的奇效。<br />\n<br />\n現時已有藥物可抑制15-PGDH，但對於人類肌肉影響的臨床研究則欠奉。<br />\n<br />\n只不過的是，現今均普遍認為增加體內細胞NAD數量的話，便可舒緩甚至是扭轉細胞的老化現象。然而，15-PGDH卻需要NAD才能正常運作，這一方面所出現的矛盾則未能解釋得到。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單俾一個like以及Bookmark，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=%2FNwPZCYHbisYOb37lcvQWife5Xzx4ME6JwL9AZsFK0I%3D&h=b7cdc33e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「買一嚿/半嚿薯仔」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=%2FNwPZCYHbisYOb37lcvQWife5Xzx4ME6JwL9AZsFK0I%3D&h=f3c98247\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n基於WhatsApp/Facebook等問題，IG將不會再作更新，只會寄居本土LIHKG及Penana。<br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://science.sciencemag.org/content/371/6528/eabc8059\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscience.sciencemag.org%2Fcontent%2F371%2F6528%2Feabc8059&d=%2FNwPZCYHbisYOb37lcvQWife5Xzx4ME6JwL9AZsFK0I%3D&h=af5a69a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://science.sciencemag.org/content/371/6528/eabc8059</a>"},{"pid":"e750ed13bdd0895cb28c8b13e315154024fe68c9","tid":2388076,"uid":203250,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T22:23:49.000Z","msg":"點解人類要進化到減少肌肉<br />\n<br />\n勞動力理論上唔係越多越好咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36f60d772137b13d80f60b893e4b0b405c9c10db","tid":2388076,"uid":212336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T22:24:12.000Z","msg":"總之操野啦"},{"pid":"b757012b877b6968517ed580deb4c02dfb727b43","tid":2388076,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e750ed13bdd0895cb28c8b13e315154024fe68c9","tid":2388076,"uid":203250,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T22:23:49.000Z","msg":"點解人類要進化到減少肌肉<br />\n<br />\n勞動力理論上唔係越多越好咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T22:25:38.000Z","msg":